      title:"Claude gets 'Reflect' — a monthly Wrapped-style recap that nudges you to log off",
      body:"Anthropic added Reflect to Claude (beta, Free/Pro/Max with memory on): a Settings dashboard showing the topics you spent time on, your most active day and peak hour, and observations about how you work with Claude, with 1–12-month lookbacks and suggestions built on Anthropic's 4D AI-fluency framework. It also adds quiet hours and take-a-break nudges; incognito chats and health-integration conversations are excluded.",
